{"tid":1709013,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"今日中環受傷果位外國人士既影片","createTime":"2019-11-11T19:37:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T06:51:21.000Z","uid":26180,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b6f71e73bc5bd8f06bce770cd65d04e42906cc81","tid":1709013,"uid":26180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T19:37:32.000Z","msg":"下午果時有手足POST左圖片出黎，但呢個係影片版本。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aG8WNsj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaG8WNsj.png&h=b2d9b947&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然影唔到中彈果下，但希望條片都對大家有用。<br />\n如果可以既話，大家可以試下搵其他影片去拼番個過程出黎。<br />\n那怕只有小小機會，話唔定咁就可以打多條國際線。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">在場所有人士只係岩岩放飯行過，就突然遇到黑警用催淚彈無差別攻擊。</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fLMxkNc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfLMxkNc.jpg&h=8d88ddf5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9069f155bb3616266b7519ba07cc97a0af17347a","tid":1709013,"uid":113724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T19:39:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9684efc6393f7e641ecb3d6068b39ef4de3ce79d","tid":1709013,"uid":60686,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T19:43:22.000Z","msg":"奶共pwc出黎講2句"},{"pid":"7a8632b6d45410c82dbcaf93047874b60950432a","tid":1709013,"uid":26180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T19:43:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"633625fd52f710eb32ef119166eb84a1e9a2bec1","tid":1709013,"uid":287772,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T19:44:40.000Z","msg":"借位一用，本人前空手道黑帶又練過詠春,又一城見到打狗後有些武術上重點一定想大家知.如果你未學過功夫：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">千祈唔好企直個人同狗不停對打。係第一時間用全身力推佢跌落地。</span></span>佢想起身再推，唔好比佢企返起身。佢跌左落地等同沒有攻擊力，唔用得槍／棍。而手足人夠多，落左地就做乜都得。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真正功夫係出幾下要打低對手，唔係不停loop出拳。（擒拿之類另計）"},{"pid":"543307570c2fcd183cbb8958836877dcb1744b60","tid":1709013,"uid":178187,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T20:30:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tVDvSdd.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtVDvSdd.gif&h=443fb6ff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1f1b88cfca0ca0e43605fec54ab14e09efc178df","tid":1709013,"uid":16864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T22:53:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49b33fa97a30b1ca34bf05afd9e971f26e17e001","tid":1709013,"uid":26180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T00:00:32.000Z","msg":"推番上黎"},{"pid":"9a5b265dba5baa822ad0b8395bad0cbd3e2d3162","tid":1709013,"uid":96871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T00:19:57.000Z","msg":"有冇第條link 好多人冇Dropbox"},{"pid":"156a82766c5456bab9c430f8ac848ee7add59296","tid":1709013,"uid":197213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"543307570c2fcd183cbb8958836877dcb1744b60","tid":1709013,"uid":178187,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T20:30:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tVDvSdd.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtVDvSdd.gif&h=443fb6ff&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:51:21.000Z","msg":"叻"}]}